  "subject": "Refactor pythonsdk_test settings",
  "commit_message": "Refactor pythonsdk_test settings\n\nUp to now, we are using the settings mechanism of python_onapsdk\nso when we need to customize pythonsdk it is not possible\nworkarounds are needed\nFor instance in basic clamp the path is needed for some clamp files.\n\nI am reusing the same code but pythonsdk_tests and python_onapsdk are\nno more linked by one single env variable.\n\nIssue-ID: TEST-290\n\nSigned-off-by: mrichomme <morgan.richomme@orange.com>\nChange-Id: Iadd4fabf5093ef03e4aa6ed945e930870cb46b9d\n",
